'''''Tasson''''' was a group of [[Delta-class DX-9 stormtrooper transport|''Delta''-class DX-9 stormtrooper transports]] based at the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] research station [[Obsidian (XQ1 Platform)|''Obsidian'']] as part of the [[TIE Experimental Project]].

When the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] attacked ''Obsidian'', Transports ''Tasson'' launched from the station to ferry pilots to [[Beta-class ETR-3 escort transport|''Beta''-class ETR-3 Escort Transport]] ''[[Suluk]]'' parked nearby, from where the pilots could control the prototype TIEs. This duty brought the transports under fire from the attacking [[A/SF-01 B-wing starfighter/Legends|B-wings]] and [[X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wings]].

All of ''Tasson'' was destroyed with the research station.

